  "body": "# Feature Issue\n### User Story\nAs a user I want to be able to quickly move all my funds, because, for example I lost my seed phrase\n\n### Description\nDesigns on [Figma](https://www.figma.com/file/XUehMnhyD1FGcWzvGz6SXqvh/Wallet?node-id=5849%3A42299)\n\n* [ ] Adds available amount in wallet for selected asset\n* [ ] In case ETH is selected, the user will need to manually edit the total to reserve some funds for gas. This design does not resolve this issue yet\n* [ ] When user taps on `Send all`\n* [ ] Amount is updated to available assets in account\n\n![1!UNITO-UNDERSCORE!1 Chat](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35233054/75551004-79b5a200-5a33-11ea-8720-43033c935cb3.png)\n\n### Acceptance Criteria\nImplementation follows design\n\n### Notes\nBest implemented after or paired with https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/10103\n\n",
